{"tid":1676614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗又一藍店","createTime":"2019-10-26T14:34:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-27T02:06:53.000Z","uid":95007,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5e320a3de87864edc4298cf22b820e0fd43bd7fe","tid":1676614,"uid":95007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日途經元朗 諗住幫襯下小店 (Chief Mind 你廚意)<br />\n因為本人係黑衫愛好者 所以當時著住黑色衫 <br />\n加上又冇洗頭 就帶左黑帽遮下頭油<br />\n當時好有禮貌咁想同職員落單<br />\n點知個職員 一嘢同我地講 收左爐 因為冇車返屋企 (當時元朗大馬路正在遍地開花) <br />\n咁唯有走啦 但係後續有人去到係照買到嘢，落到單，個廚師仲煮緊麵架。<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為我年輕又著黑衫，所以叔叔唔賣嘢食比我呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求fact check 係咪藍店<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KRNijYG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKRNijYG.png&h=86d396d3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"61a535d39271cbd872fdea947cab9a2a0c5630fe","tid":1676614,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:35:20.000Z","msg":"【黃色經濟】有個傻仔整咗個黃藍商鋪認證平台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eqgeNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eqgeNS</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2afb057368ff26400d3c955340538fbe4466123b","tid":1676614,"uid":274538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T14:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URX6tUK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURX6tUK.jpg&h=d6f8c1df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TpDUCN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTpDUCN5.jpg&h=4591481c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cJV0ymr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcJV0ymr.jpg&h=90f9031b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6MBbE1s.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6MBbE1s.gif&h=223f43d7&s={SIZE}\" />"